The classes in this package are dedicated to improve an annotation using various methods.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MutualDisambiguation
    This class receives an WikimetaXMLDecoder Annotated Object, retrieves all the DBPedia or Wikipedia content for each link, and uses them to disambiguate.
    NormalizeNE
    Normalize NE in a document.
    SimpleCoreferenceDetector
    This is a simple coreference detector and resolution tool utilized to correct coreference clusters for PERS, ORG and GPE.

Package nlp.upperlevel Description

The classes in this package are dedicated to improve an annotation using various methods. They are applied on a previously annotated object from Wikimeta. Please note that those classes are only compatible with WikiMetaXMLDecoder object. The WikiMetaJSONDecoder did not receive all the methods required to apply those methods.
See Also:
